21
00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:33.000
Now this user has read and write access to the "test" repository;

22
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:37.733
this allows the " jasongtaylor " account to directly edit this repository

23
00:01:37.733 --> 00:01:42.066
and accept pull requests into this repository. Alright, let's check it out.

24
00:01:42.066 --> 00:01:45.200
So, I'm going to head back over to the "jasongtaylor" profile;

25
00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:48.100
